Welcome to the libnetvirt library. The library to virtualize your network.
Author: Daniel Turull KTH Royal Institute of Technology <danieltt@kth.se>

Tested on Ubuntu 11.10

Pre-requisites:
autoconf
libtool
libxml2-dev
swig
build-essential
pkg-config
python-all-dev



Interface with PyOCNI:
* Python=2.7
* Python-all-dev (for eventlet/greenlet install)
* python-setuptools (to execute the setup.py file)


Installing with OpenFlow nox controller (nox or nox11oflib)


Pre-requisites:
autoconf 
automake 
g++
libtool
swig
make
git-core
libboost-dev
libboost-test-dev
libboost-filesystem-dev
libssl-dev
libpcap-dev
python-twisted
libboost-dev

Compiling:
cd nox11oflib or cd nox
./boot.sh
mkdir build
cd build
../configure
make

Running FNS with NOX
cd src
 ./nox_core -i ptcp: fns

Enjoy :-)
